1. Ona *vara* svoju sestru stalno. (She's deceiving her sister constantly.)
2. Ja ne mogu da verujem da me *varaš*. (I can't believe you're cheating on me.)
3. Oni su bili uhapšeni zbog *varanja* na ispitu. (They were arrested for cheating on the exam.)
4. Kupio sam ovu mašinu, ali mislim da su me *varali* sa cenom. (I bought this machine, but I think they ripped me off with the price.)
5. Ne volim da *varim* svoje prijatelje. (I don't like to deceive my friends.)
6. Koliko *vara* ova vaga? (How much does this scale deceive?)
7. Da li ti se čini da *varaju* sa brojem zaraženih? (Do you think they're falsifying the number of infected?)
8. Oni su *varalice* koji pokušavaju da prevari druge. (They are deceivers who try to cheat others.)
9. Ja ne volim da se *varaju* ljudi oko mene. (I don't like people to be deceived around me.)
10. Iako je on *varao* u prošlosti, sada je iskren. (Although he cheated in the past, he's honest now.)